
# ServicesInMyCity

**The first production app on the EMG Loop platform.**

Rocco is your friendly, honest local repair guide for the Jersey Shore. Built with Astro, React, and Anthropic Claude, with Netlify Functions handling the server-side AI and rate limiting.

## Local Development

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 20+ (check `.nvmrc`)
- npm 10+

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/elitemediagroup1/servicesinmycity.git
cd servicesinmycity

# Install dependencies (check package.json for pinned versions)
npm install

# Create a .env.local file from .env.example and fill in your secrets
cp .env.example .env.local
# Edit .env.local with your API keys (see section below)
```

### Running Locally

```bash
# Start dev server (Astro dev mode)
npm run dev

# Build for production (static output + Netlify functions)
npm run build

# Preview production build locally
npm run preview
```

The dev server runs on `http://localhost:3000` by default.

## Environment Variables

**Never commit real secrets.** All sensitive values go in Netlify dashboard or your `.env.local` (not in Git).

### Required for Full Functionality

| Variable | Purpose | Example / Notes |
|----------|---------|-----------------|
| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | Rocco AI (Claude) | Get from https://console.anthropic.com |
| `ROCCO_MODEL` | Model for Rocco responses | Default: `claude-sonnet-4-20250514` (Sonnet-class, no Opus in prod) |
| `ROCCO_MODEL_FALLBACK` | Fallback model if primary is unavailable | Default: `claude-haiku-4-20250514` |
| `GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY` | Local discovery (Google Places Text Search) | Get from Google Cloud Console |
| `SESSION_SECRET` | Session encryption (server-side only) | Any strong random string |
| `DAILY_SPEND_CEILING_USD` | Max AI spend per day | Default: `25` |
| `RATE_LIMIT_SESSION` | Requests per session per minute | Default: `30` |
| `RATE_LIMIT_IP` | Requests per IP per minute | Default: `120` |
| `ARS_HANDOFF_ENDPOINT` | A.J. Perri HVAC lead handoff | Leave empty in Phase 1; add URL when ready |
| `PUBLIC_GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID` | Google Analytics 4 ID (public) | Default: `G-YR9GML8439` (ServicesInMyCity only) |

### Security Notes

- **Secrets are server-side only.** The browser never receives `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` or `GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY`.
- **GA4 ID is public** (`PUBLIC_` prefix) — it's safe and expected to be visible in client-side scripts.
- In Netlify, set real values in **Settings > Environment variables**. Never set them in Git.

## Deploy to Netlify

### Checklist Before Merging to Main

- [ ] All tests pass locally: `npm run build` completes without errors
- [ ] GA4 is working (check Analytics in production)
- [ ] Rocco AI is responding (test `/api/rocco` with valid API key)
- [ ] Local discovery returns honest results (no fabricated listings)
- [ ] ARS handoff stub is in place (no real leads sent unless endpoint configured)
- [ ] Sitemap is generated (`/sitemap-index.xml` accessible)
- [ ] Robots.txt is in place (`/robots.txt` blocks `/api/*`)
- [ ] All environment variables are set in Netlify dashboard (not committed)

### Deployment Steps

1. **Merge to `main`** (PR must be approved)
2. **Netlify auto-deploys** from the `main` branch
3. **Verify in production:**
   - Visit https://servicesinmycity.com
   - Check DevTools > Network for GA4 requests
   - Test `/ask` page (Rocco chat)
   - Check Netlify Functions logs for errors

### Rollback

If something breaks:
1. Revert the commit on `main`
2. Netlify will re-deploy within seconds
3. Check Functions logs: https://app.netlify.com/sites/[site-name]/functions

## Known Caveats

### Phase 1 (Current)

1. **In-Memory Rate Limit Counters:** Reset on function cold start. Each deploy clears counters.
   - **Mitigation:** Counters reset daily and per-session anyway; perfect for MVP.
   - **Phase 2:** Replace with Netlify Blobs for persistence across cold starts.

2. **ARS Handoff is Stubbed:** No real lead data is sent unless `ARS_HANDOFF_ENDPOINT` is configured in Netlify.
   - **Mitigation:** Consent gate is in place; modal clearly explains data usage.
   - **Testing:** Test flow works end-to-end; just doesn't actually forward anywhere yet.

3. **Google Places Discovery Only:** Results are honest. No recommendations or rankings.
   - **Behavior:** Empty results when no matches (no fabrication).
   - **Scope:** Jersey Shore only (by design).

4. **Model IDs May Need Updates:** Anthropic periodically deprecates older models.
   - **Monitoring:** Watch Anthropic API status; update `ROCCO_MODEL` if needed.
   - **Graceful Fallback:** If primary model is unavailable, system returns soft limit (honest "not available now").

### Architecture Notes

- **Static-first:** Astro generates static HTML + CSS; only Rocco chat island hydrates React.
- **Secrets server-side:** Netlify Functions are the only gateway to Anthropic and Google APIs.
- **Progressive enhancement:** Page works without JavaScript; chat is island-only enhancement.
- **Session identity:** Anonymous; no personal data is stored long-term.
- **Consent gate:** ARS handoff respects explicit user consent before any lead is forwarded.

